data.description: Seller Incentive, reduce buyers interest rate up to 3% for 3 years with a temporary interest rate buy down. Now your dream home is more affordable! This beautifully renovated brick cape cod offers the perfect blend of modern luxury and comfortable living. Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood in Matindale Meadows, this charming 3 bedroom, 2 full bathroom, living room, and full finished basement offers additional living space. Fenced in yard with full sized storage shed for additional storage workspace. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a newly renovated home in the heart of Harrison Township. Embrace the comfort, style, and convenience this property has to offer. Schedule your private tour today and turn your homeownership dreams into reality.
